    "description": "Asmo Corporation processed, imports and sells meat products in Japan, Taiwan, and China. It operates through ASMO Business; ASMO Trading Business; ASMO Food Services Business; ASMO service business; ASMO nursing care service business; and ASMOCATERING (HK) business. It provides meals in various fields, such as hospital meals, office meals, school meals, and welfare facility meals for the elderly. The company also offers nursing care services; manages 10 Japanese restaurants in Hong Kong; and provides insurance products. Additionally, it engages in trust business, such as management of property for the elderly and maintenance of lump-sum payment for paid elderly home, as well as real estate leasing business. Further, the company operates home-visit and care establishments, pay nursing homes, and restaurants. The company was incorporated in 1975 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan. Asmo Corporation operates as a subsidiary of PersonsBridge Co., Ltd."
